{"tid":2410863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利研究︰近兩成新冠肺炎男性康復者無精子","createTime":"2021-02-17T03:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T10:35:05.000Z","uid":36494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"975401cb4b57dc0c70e0dcc7545001290e9581fc","tid":2410863,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:03:18.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎肆虐全球，康復後的後遺症亦惹來不少人關注。早前義大利佛羅倫斯大學一項研究顯示，部份罹患新冠肺炎的男性康復後，出現精子數量減少情況。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員分析了 43 名年齡介於 30 至 65 歲感染新冠病毒男性的精液樣本<br />\n<br />\n這些男性康復一個月後，25% 男性精子數量較低，近 20% 的男性存在無精症<br />\n<br />\n研究也發現，部分新冠治療藥物可能影響精子數量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2878666?fbclid=IwAR2KF18PW_pqOdlS5BWzwlxtn8HJFVoX6_zsnwB82N90diXWl6E2lub-jJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2878666%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2KF18PW_pqOdlS5BWzwlxtn8HJFVoX6_zsnwB82N90diXWl6E2lub-jJA&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=b92e2592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2878666?fbclid=IwAR2KF18PW_pqOdlS5BWzwlxtn8HJFVoX6_zsnwB82N90diXWl6E2lub-jJA</a>"},{"pid":"567af27dfad0371eb6b9cdfbc4dcf09875829d44","tid":2410863,"uid":7147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"慳唔小錢"},{"pid":"8f66172ee2fd59f43211975e369121c9bd94fd06","tid":2410863,"uid":392206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"正喎，可以以後大條道理打真軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28597f2c4b1e63876a836f618336695d614340ec","tid":2410863,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"唔使買 dom dom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c23ede44ae1e066f9cc95732017a5b9faec81f","tid":2410863,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f66172ee2fd59f43211975e369121c9bd94fd06","tid":2410863,"uid":392206,"like":3,"dislike